{"tid":682723,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"還可以走多遠？","createTime":"2018-05-29T05:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T02:57:12.000Z","uid":61,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb675c0813a3c462f734a44a685390468c0774b8","tid":682723,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"有無人會有感覺感情去到某一個位，<br />\n覺得自己無能力再一時三刻變得更好，<br />\n但對方就好似繼續為左你而努力變得更好，<br />\n覺得隨時就會有其他人嚟搶走佢咁，<br />\n佢肯定可以輕易接觸到一個比我好更多嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n一諗到會咁，個人好自然就會好驚好無助，<br />\n事業同成就唔會因為一時三刻嘅時間就有，<br />\n但其他人就已經事業有成咁去接觸你嘅伴侶。<br />\n<br />\n你嬲但無得表示於人前，<br />\n你驚但唔可以被佢知道，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解偏偏係你大過我而唔係我大過你...<br />\n<br />\n只能一直處於被動嘅一方嗎？<br />\n<br />\n求爸絲解答，家庭背景相差懸殊，佢富我貧"},{"pid":"4d249fd0a21a9420f43975d7d62e7373c289168c","tid":682723,"uid":59569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"一場跑唔完既長跑"},{"pid":"24c24cc7f978eaf005bfd6736e6153b51734f759","tid":682723,"uid":61,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"好辛苦...每日都會驚"},{"pid":"75a1424fa91c272dc7fd525707d79b76967d2760","tid":682723,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ffab09d732c3657fc9e57214e9db284ff67f12f","tid":682723,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75a1424fa91c272dc7fd525707d79b76967d2760","tid":682723,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:26:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T06:31:25.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cebe372f8d77a538619b48c8ab956b30e99f10a","tid":682723,"uid":61,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"可愛的點是？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3c2fd4c880ad1638401194e22c1b101db76d19","tid":682723,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci